[normal]period last year
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]It noted that trusts are finding it increasingly difficult to deliver efficiency savings and that some of those reporting deficits have not done so before. 
[normal]It also noted that
[normal] many 
[normal]of those planning a surplus 
[normal]are 
[normal]forecasting that this will be le
[normal]ss than 2.5 per cent of income, 
[normal]suggesting that
